                  </persName>
            ,</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17910216-41-verdict264" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910216-41-verdict264" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Each to be <rs id="t17910216-41-punish265" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910216-41-punish265" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910216-41-defend511 t17910216-41-punish265"></join>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910216-41-defend513 t17910216-41-punish265"></join>
               imprisoned six months
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17910216-41-punish266" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910216-41-punish266" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17910216-41-punish266" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="sureties"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910216-41-defend511 t17910216-41-punish266"></join>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910216-41-defend513 t17910216-41-punish266"></join>
               find security for six months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
